Swing Arm City, Utah - In his latest display of Hoonigan theatrics, Ken Block ditches his usual urban jungle scene to kick up some dust in a Utah desert. In fact, given the terrain differences, the gymkhana star found a new name for his latest action video: Terrakhana. Anyhow, the Pennzoil-sponsored gig saw Block put his 447kW Ford Fiesta ST RX43 rally car through its paces, up dunes and all and in soaring heat, in the vicinity of Swing Arm City in Utah. Crank up the volume, and enjoy...   IOL Motoring